    dc:description "FIGURES 2 − 7. Adults of Phalonidia spp. 2. Labial palpus of Phalonidia affinitana tauriana (Kennel); 3. P. affinitana tauriana (Kennel), Ƥ; 4. P. aliena Kuznetzov, 3; 5. P. brevifasciaria, sp. nov., holotype, 3; 6. P. chlorolitha (Meyrick), 3; 7. P. contractana (Zeller), 3." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/224142/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.224145>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20 – 25. Male genitalia of Phalonidia spp. 20. P. aliena Kuznetzov, slide no. SYH 11063; 21. P. brevifasciaria, sp. nov., holotype, slide no. SYH 10224; 22. P. chlorolitha (Meyrick), slide no. SYH 11664; 23. P. contractana (Zeller), slide no. SYH 11020; 24. P. c o re a n a Byun & Li, slide no. SYH 11025; 25. P. curvistrigana (Stainton), slide no. SYH 11390." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/224145/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.224148>
    dc:description "FIGURES 36 – 41. Female genitalia of Phalonidia spp. 36. P. affinitana tauriana (Kennel), slide no. SYH 11657; 37. P. chlorolitha (Meyrick), slide no. SYH 10206; 38. P. contractana (Zeller), slide no. MZ 96147; 39. P. c o re a n a Byun & Li, slide no. SYH 11032; 40. P. curvistrigana (Stainton), slide no. SYH 11035; 41. P. f r a t e r n a Razowski, slide no. SYH 11033." ;
