    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.224143>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 13. Adults of Phalonidia spp. 8. P. c o re a n a Byun & Li, Ƥ; 9. P. curvistrigana (Stainton), 3; 10. P. f r a t e r n a Razowski, Ƥ; 11. P. latifasciana Razowski, 3; 12. P. l y d i a e (Filipjev), Ƥ; 13. P. melanothicta (Meyrick), 3." ;
